      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Dear Dr. Hynek:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Your article entitled \"The UFO Mystery,\" which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "you prepared for the FBI Law Enforcement Bulletin, has been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "published in the February, 1975, edition and begins on page 16.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "I am sure that the information contained in this interesting article",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "will be of value to law enforcement officers throughout the country,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "and my associates and I want to take this opportunity to express",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "our appreciation for your cooperation.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Several advance copies of the Bulletin are enclosed,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "and I shall be glad to see that additional ones are sent to you if",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "desired.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
